### ============================================================
### argus-agents REST API — VS Code REST Client
###
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Install VS Code extension: "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
###   2. Set DEV_MODE=true and run the server:
###        cd backend && uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
###   3. Obtain a JWT:
###        • Option A (recommended): run `POST /auth/callback` request below,
###          copy the `token` value from the response, paste it into
###          the `YOUR_TOKEN_HERE` placeholder below, and remove this comment.
###        • Option B: open http://localhost:8000/docs and use "Try it out".
###
### Usage: click "Send Request" above any `###`-delimited block.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE   # ← paste JWT here after obtaining it

# ── Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### POST /auth/callback — Dev login (get JWT)
# Copy the "token" value from the response body into @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/callback?code=dev&state=dev
X-Dev-User: alice

### GET /auth/login — Initiate OIDC flow (prod only; in dev mode redirects to callback)
# In production, this redirects to the OIDC provider. Set DEV_MODE=false to test.
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/login?redirect_uri=/

# ── Users ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /users/me — Get current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PATCH /users/me — Update current user name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Alice Updated" }

# ── Internal Providers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /internal-providers — List system-level providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal-providers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── User Providers ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /providers — List current user's providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST /providers — Create a new LLM provider
POST {{baseUrl}}/providers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My OpenAI",
  "config": {
    "api_key": "sk-test123456789",
    "base_url": "https://api.openai.com",
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
  }
}

### PUT /providers/{id}/default — Set a provider as default
# Replace {{provider_id}} with an actual provider UUID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/providers/{{provider_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### DELETE /providers/{id} — Delete a provider association
# Replace {{provider_id}} with an actual provider UUID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/providers/{{provider_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
